The Oblitercons:


::Dark One and his minions retreated, heading for the Alliance base::
"What's that!" Dark One yelled as he spotted a Maximal craft.

::The Oblitercons approached to investigate, scanners saying no one was home, 
but the door was open::

::Breakdown and Hiss stepped in, weapons in the air, yelling that it was 
clear::

::Dark One and his men began to search the ship, except for Pyro who was 
still unconsciouss, unknown to them this was the ship which Double Punch, 
Injector, Manterror and Stinkbomb arrived on::
